{"tid":1970079,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許冠傑演唱會團隊逾4人  食物及衞生局：會否違限聚令視乎實際情況","createTime":"2020-04-13T01:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T02:34:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a10431047205547fa66ed0746751faec7a1059bb","tid":1970079,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:20:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RGpQL4DTRVjswPgZASn2ew--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/d0f3d7f0-7d18-11ea-adcc-ababb834327a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRGpQL4DTRVjswPgZASn2ew--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2Fd0f3d7f0-7d18-11ea-adcc-ababb834327a&h=330c59b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歌手許冠傑昨日下午在尖沙咀一個商場的天台，以網上直播形式舉辦演唱會，製作團隊超過4人。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局說，禁止人群聚集規例列明，「在工作地點為工作而進行的群組聚集」可獲豁免，豁免是否適用於演唱會製作單位拍攝節目，視乎當時實際情況及工作性質，例如公眾能否進入，參加者是否有工作指示等。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥與官員開會期間，亦有透過視像欣賞演唱會。她認為，粵語流行曲仍然大有可為，香港的高質素演唱會，將會是經濟邁向復蘇的重要元素，康文署會與演出業協會商量，如何在疫情過後，在場地安排及場租方面提供支援。"},{"pid":"8568330803e3461586f5ca7167a8a7a77723a8cd","tid":1970079,"uid":118716,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"叫何韻詩、黃耀明整返場睇下點"},{"pid":"743311f11795e0947c928ea97217b8b752578a6b","tid":1970079,"uid":246023,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府永遠一個邏輯<br />\n<br />\n總之我話違反就違反<br />\n冇就冇"},{"pid":"908dddb56c22c2cd92fc263279ede1b876f52649","tid":1970079,"uid":54633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T01:46:50.000Z","msg":"實際上咪就係多過4個"},{"pid":"d8739c185811e1e609eb399fcabf76fad558c489","tid":1970079,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"即係由執法單位自行決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor